a999713c1352fb","tid":1885241,"uid":29188,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"有閪外匯買西藥咩，所以咪焗住用中藥囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲吓要用巫醫咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"香爐灰水，符水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d15ad4ccc465d4f63cf5894ce5e5274659d9ac4","tid":1885241,"uid":39258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6fa58a48ef65a0e238c776daeef39b64bdce2d3","tid":1885241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpPA0vnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpPA0vnh.jpg&h=41ddd030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎疫情延燒，中國國家主席習近平指示治療要結合中西醫，醫療部門開始推動中藥治療，根據湖北省衛生健康委員會數據，湖北的中藥使用率已超過8成，並指患者病情有顯著改善。但也有美國專家認為，中藥能否治療武漢肺炎，還需審慎評估。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，湖北省衛健委指出，自疫情爆發以來，該省堅持使用中西醫結合的方式治療患者。截至2月16日，全省225間指定醫院，58182例確診病例中，中藥使用率已達83.3%，武漢市則為80%，患者病情有顯著改善者，總效率為81.3%。目前，由中醫團隊主導的江夏方艙醫院，運用針灸、按摩、灸療、太極拳、八段錦等「中國特色」療法，加上因人施治的湯藥，治療武漢肺炎患者。<br />\n<br />\n除了官方，中國媒體、專家也宣傳中醫治療武漢肺炎的療效，官媒《環球時報》訪問各中醫師說法，其中湖北省中醫院隔離病房肺五科主任馮毅表示，「中藥在對腹瀉、便秘等腸胃症狀發揮了很大的作用」、「實際上，中醫治療某些疾病效果很快，中醫也有不少針對急診的療法，而且副作用較小」，但每個受訪中醫師仍強調，中西醫要並重，不能只靠中醫治療。<br />\n<br />\n而根據《美國之音》報導，美國食品與藥物管理局（FDA）資深專家方國棟受訪時指出，武漢肺炎重症患者不可能單獨使用中醫及中藥來治療，中醫的療效仍待審慎評估；美國馬里蘭大學醫學院的醫師張英華則表示，中藥不能直接對抗病毒，只能用於輔助和支持治療，或是在恢復階段時，加入中藥調理「可能會有效果」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3071691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071691&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=e2b01671\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071691&h=2618ba16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3071691</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:14:07.000Z","msg":"班人都死撚哂，究竟係咩人食緊藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2182f59d1a0fcb7583c3e6281a6d41accd1421e","tid":1885241,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28dfa8c34e0c3900f4eef94688926416fa552aee","tid":1885241,"uid":83328,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"做咩手術呀?<br />\n刮骨療傷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"刮肺療毒"},{"pid":"4f6645a51ee5f3aa40117b3621cc88b83a630d91","tid":1885241,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"佢咳到咁樣 點落針呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248c345da72c654c88df73cc57e02ae5fcd9ccf7","tid":1885241,"uid":137159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得湖北死亡率咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b022b58e326133165dfa95e0d93f959c2d5901","tid":1885241,"uid":24641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"香爐灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23f74067dc37a8966bed1eedfe3f2c57634c60a","tid":1885241,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356416796c3e85a134d0cf7243c6a7b43a515100","tid":1885241,"uid":339472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"用完中藥咪攞去燒囉"},{"pid":"67c2b8cde02495f2c3151b21f0a9084f42b41108","tid":1885241,"uid":145837,"like":0,"dislik